As bad as it sounds... I have to say that while it would be nice if they spoke in a universal tounge, they shouldn't have to by any means. At times this could be quite a bit of trouble in certain areas, but it adds some elements... such as a person whom knows other languages could translate. <br>
<br>
It may seem unfair, and it may feel like you are being left out of a GM event, but it is one of the cons to this server and to the language barriers that are in place. We all accept these rules by playing here. Personally, yes the language barriers can be a pain, but I also think that they can be fun and do add to the atmosphere of the world...<br>
<br>
